==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Megaric
<hw>Me*gar"ic</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <def>Belonging, or pertaining, to
Megara, a city of ancient Greece.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Megarian school</b></col>, <it>or</it>
<col><b>Megaric school</b></col></mcol>, <cd>a school of philosophy
established at <city>Megara</city>, after the death of Socrates, by his
disciples, and remarkable for its logical subtlety.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

